decision_details:
- the proposal made by Hon. Dinesh Gunawardena, Minister of Water Supply and Drainage, to award the following contracts as recommended by the Standing Cabinet Appointed Procurement Committee (SCAPC), was approved by the Cabinet:

*	Contract for Towns East of Colombo District Water Supply Project - Package 1;

*	Contract for Ruhunupura Distribution Water Supply Project ;

*	Contract for Ampara Distribution Network Water Supply Project; and

*	Contract for Bentota Water Supply Project.
